---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jai Long Case Study | Dino Favara Jr."
  description="From 400 average views to 655K total views in 60 days. Built the entire content identity from scratch — positioning, format library, and a podcast-to-short-form pipeline."
>
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <!-- Back link -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10">
      <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary/70 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
        &larr; All case studies
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-700 tracking-wide mb-6">
        Brand Build from Zero
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-dark mb-4">
        Jai Long Co.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-light text-dark/60 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        From 400 average views to 655K total views in 60 days — built from a blank content slate.
      </p>

      <!-- Service tags -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
        {['Content Identity', 'Brand Positioning', 'Format Library', 'Podcast Clips', 'Short-Form Pipeline'].map(tag => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-dark/10 bg-white/60 text-xs font-medium text-dark/55">
            {tag}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Before / After -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/70 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr]">
          <!-- Before -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Avg Views Before</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-red-500">400</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">per video</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Arrow -->
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center px-4">
            <span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&rarr;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex md:hidden items-center justify-center py-2">
            <span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&darr;</span>
          </div>
          <!-- After -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center bg-periwinkle/6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Total Views After</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-primary">655K</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">in 60 days</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Metrics Grid -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '655K', label: 'Total Views', sub: '(in 60 days)' },
          { value: '1,638x', label: 'View Increase', sub: '(vs. baseline)' },
          { value: '0→1', label: 'Content Identity', sub: '(built from scratch)' },
          { value: '60', label: 'Days to Results', sub: '(fastest ramp)' },
        ].map(m => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-5 text-center">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl text-primary">{m.value}</span>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/45">{m.label}</p>
            <p class="mt-0.5 text-[10px] text-dark/35">{m.sub}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Body Content -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
      <article class="prose-custom">
        <h3>The Situation</h3>
        <p>Jai Long is a photographer, educator, and founder of Jai Long Co. — a business built around helping photographers build sustainable creative careers. He had credibility, a podcast, and real expertise. But his short-form content wasn't cutting through. Average views sat around 400 per video, and there was no clear content identity tying everything together.</p>

        <h3>The Approach</h3>
        <p>This was a build-from-scratch engagement. Before touching a single format, I did the positioning work: <strong>who is Jai Long online, what does he own, and what does a cold viewer instantly understand about him?</strong></p>
        <p>We landed on a clear thesis and built a format library designed to express it consistently. I also architected a podcast-to-short-form pipeline that let Jai extract short-form content from his existing long-form episodes without doubling his workload. Every clip was chosen and structured to do two things: hook a cold viewer and reinforce his positioning.</p>
        <p>The goal wasn't to post more. It was to post with purpose — every video in service of a single, recognizable brand.</p>

        <h3>The Results</h3>
        <p>In 60 days, Jai generated 655K total views — starting from a 400 view baseline. That's a 1,638x increase. More importantly, he had a system he could run. A format library. A clear identity. A pipeline from podcast to short-form that didn't require starting over every week.</p>
        <p>The speed of the ramp was unusual. 60 days is the fastest I've seen a brand go from near-zero to a consistent six-figure view cadence. That's what happens when the identity work comes before the content work.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-dark/8">
        <span class="text-sm font-light text-dark/45">Timeline: 60 days</span>
        <div class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-full rounded-full bg-dark/6 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-periwinkle to-mint" style="width: 100%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Back to Work CTA -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-xl text-dark">Want results like this?</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-dark/55 mt-1">Let's talk about building your content engine.</p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="mailto:dino@mercurysocialmedia.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-primary text-off-white font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95 whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          Email me &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom h3 {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-custom h3:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .prose-custom p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.65);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-custom strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  .prose-custom blockquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    background: rgba(107, 92, 231, 0.04);
    border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0;
  }
  .prose-custom blockquote p {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .prose-custom blockquote cite {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.45);
  }
</style>
